ORDER
The state’s motion to dismiss this appeal is assigned to the motion calendar for Monday, May 5, 1980 at 9:30 a. m. for oral argument.

attorneys: Dennis J. Roberts II, Atty. Gen., Stephen Lichatin III, Spec. Asst. Atty. Gen., Chief, Appellate Division, for plaintiff.
John F. Cicilline, Providence, for defendant.
casebody.head_matter:
STATE v. Ronald BROWN.

March 20, 1980.
Dennis J. Roberts II, Atty. Gen., Stephen Lichatin III, Spec. Asst. Atty. Gen., Chief, Appellate Division, for plaintiff.
John F. Cicilline, Providence, for defendant.
